title: People Holding Hands Medium Light Skin Tone Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Two people holding hands, with one person having a medium-light skin tone and the other having a medium-dark skin tone. Represents connection, partnership, and love between individuals of different complexions.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji beautifully depicts two individuals holding hands, their skin tones a harmonious blend of medium-light and medium-dark, showcasing Apple's inclusive design approach. The hands are rendered with soft rounded edges and subtle 3D shading, suggesting a gentle, supportive connection. This symbol of unity, partnership, and friendship is a warm and welcoming addition to Apple communications.
